entry.title: gematik/spec-E-Rezept-ServiceRequest
entry.summary: The e-prescription request concept is intended to demonstrate a way of sending and receiving messages in the context of the e-prescription in a decentralized manner between the participants. The messages are strongly structured and prepared in FHIR bundles.
